"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## \\n\\n![Mundo Lingo Ambassador at work in Oslo ](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2KDjVn9uTrSZKckCjPLGI.png?height=468&width=1397)\\n\\n## The Art of Introducing People\\n\\nThe easiest way to help **loners** to socialise may surprise you.\\n\\n**RolePlay |** Here we have 2 people. ‚Äú**Loner**‚Äù and ‚Äú**Match**‚Äù\\n\\n1. Approach **Loner**, ask their name, make light conversation.\\n2. Ask ‚Äú*There are other speakers of your language in this event, can I introduce you?*‚Äù\\n3. If **Loner** say yes, ask them to wait there *(not follow you)* while you go to talk with the **match**. The **match** should be someone, or some people who are standing and have similar flags.\\n4. Ask **Match** (or **matches**) if you can introduce someone to them. If **Match** say yes, ask their name and tell them to wait there *(not follow you)*.\\n5. Return to the **Loner** and ask them to follow you. Escort **Loner** to the **Match**.\\n6. Introduce **Match** and **Loner** by name.\\n7. Now‚Ä¶.  run away! üò± Go! Don‚Äôt even say anything, just get out of there!\\n\\n### Why??\\n\\nIt may feel bad randomly running away but it works. Giving them the privacy to meet each other without the feeling of you watching is **waaay** easier. If you feel too bad, just say *‚ÄúExcuse me, I‚Äôll be right back‚Äù* and exit. You don‚Äôt actually have to come back. However you do it, don‚Äôt wait around while they meet each other, it only makes it more awkward.\\n\\n## Now what?\\n\\nNext up, how to be a [Vulture Hunter](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/kQBwhQlTdsO8KCXfgG3OJn_ej4pmC5ZUCfOlrKvzIsM) üèπ\\n\\n### Go Back\\n\\nüëà [Ambassador‚Äôs Guild](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/1dLDLYhEaAbuzsJXAXt4JE62ZNLwCJnFLWRXbRjBqUY)\",\"timestamp\":1639557608,\"title\":\"A Cupids Guide\"},\"digest\":\"k9BKt_zNbzM5r5jolZqxtL7C9MooU98lhp02Rh0XEDg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"RpIIM_7EImYsF5Av1mA9mE1X-F8fA-u1l_6O40AIV2jN5lwzcsURyInqpypUajbIAKgJ7WLNHb1G5ZoL6JH3uw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x57d0f7cbea22222afabed23e09ac819f759269ea4cca2a83cdd992ddf3ffe88d22a7afd325b70c3c1ae7dee6f5fc8e22188ba69c589cf1f0528e258261121ae51b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"sKQAXOKMUR7ruynT8iHu8IuCxI9kruvjl0cWp75AROI\"}"